metadata.name: The Destin West Jetty
metadata.description:
The sun sets as beach fishers enjoy the white sand beaches of Destin, Florida, piling up freshly caught Redfish and Pampano into their igloos as they pack up for the evening.

Date: April 10, 2019  4:58pm  
Location: The West Jetty in Destin, Florida  
Coordinates: 30.385516, -86.515147  
Camera: Canon EOS 5D Mark III
